public static final class ExerTypeVoidImplCollection.VoidSubmissionDataStatsGiver<E extends ExerciseData,S extends SubmissionInfo>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SubmissionStatisticsGiver<E,S>

Empty implementation for the SubmissionStatisticsGiver that can be used with any implementor of the SubmissionInfo-interface.

Only displays a localized message stating that "Submission statistics viewer is not implemented for the exercise type".

In principle SubmissionStatisticsGiver can be implemented later than an exercise-type is used meaning that this class can be useful even in real ViLLE-ready exercise-types.
